<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_13_r1l2"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> Als vns ewr vveiſheit <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>verſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd v̈mb etlıche </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_13_r1l4"> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> Rates 
<del rend="strikethrough">eu </del> gebeten hat euch <expan>ʒuleih<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auf den Recht 
<del rend="strikethrough"> age </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_13_r1l3"><expan>lich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tag </ab></add> den der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_13_r1l5"><expan>hoch<ex>wirdig</ex></expan> fürſt vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> her <expan>Joh<ex>an</ex></expan> <expan>Burggr<ex>af</ex></expan> cʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_13_r1l6">Otingen vnd euch her gen <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> auf den Suntag vor dem <expan>heẏlige<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_13_r1l7">pfingſtag ſchierſt geſecʒt hat / Alſo vvöllen vvir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> Erſamkeit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_13_r1l8">die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> cʒu <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tag gern <expan>leih<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd ſchicken . <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wo vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_13_r1l9">ewr erſamen <expan>freuntſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> in den <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>ſach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lieb oder dinſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_13_r1l10">beweıſen <expan>möhte<ex>n</ex></expan> des <expan>w<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vvir wıllig vnd teten das <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_13_r1l11"><expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ıııȷ̃ <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>do<ex>min</ex>ıcam</expan> Cantate Anno </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_13" id="5v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
